Insider Activity


Individual




Angela J. Ahrendts



Ms. Angela J. Ahrendts is Senior Vice President-Retail & Online Stores at Apple, Inc.
Ms. Ahrendts was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer & Executive Director by Burberry Group Plc, Executive Vice President by Fifth & Pacific Cos., Inc., Executive Vice President by Henri Bendel, Inc., Executive Vice President-Henri Bendel by Limited Brands, Inc., and President by Donna Karan International, Inc.
She received her undergraduate degree from Ball State University (Indiana).



