Angela Ahrendts - Wikipedia





















 






Angela Ahrendts

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Angela Ahrendts
DBE


Born
Angela Jean Ahrendts
(1960-06-07) June 7, 1960 (age 57)
New Palestine, Indiana, U.S.


Residence
California
London, United Kingdom


Other names
